    <h1>Crawl Error</h1>
    <p class="description">Any failure that stops a search-engine crawler from fetching a URL. Split into <strong>site-level errors</strong> (DNS, server 5xx) and <strong>URL-level errors</strong> (404, soft 404, 403). Both drain crawl budget and delay indexing.</p>
